---------------------------------------------------
-- Running an integration test from command line --
---------------------------------------------------

1. First build the project
--------------------------
$ mvn clean install -DskipTests


2. Navigate to target folder and locate the jar file
----------------------------------------------------
$ cd csp-apps/integration-tests/target


3. Run one or more test-classes by providing the package+classnames as arguments
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
$ java -jar integration-tests-0.2.0-SNAPSHOT.jar com.intrasoft.csp.integration.sandbox.server.internal.CspServerInternalSandboxTest

APPENDIX
--------

Sample with docker profile and env vars

java -jar -Dspring.profiles.active=docker -DES_PATH_BASE=/pathbse -DES_PORT=9000 -DES_LOCAL_DOMAIN=es.local -DIL_SSL_KEYSTORE_PASS=123456 -DIL_SSL_KEY_PASS=12345 -DIL_CSP_SUBDOMAIN_PREFIX=pref -DTC_PATH_TEAMS=/teams  -DTC_PATH_CIRCLES=/circles -DCSP_NAME -DTC_LOCAL_DOMAIN=tc.local  integration-tests-0.2.0-SNAPSHOT.jar com.intrasoft.csp.integration.business.server.internal.CspServerInternalBusinessTcTest


USEFUL Docker commands
----------------------

$ docker exec -i -t csp-il  /bin/sh

USEFUL CURLs
------------

For alpine distros:
apk --no-cache add curl

curl -v -s -k --key /opt/ssl/server/csp-internal.key --cert /opt/ssl/server/csp-internal.crt -H "Content-Type: application/json" -X POST -d @data.json https://integration.local.demo1-csp.athens.intrasoft-intl.private/v1/dsl/integrationData

curl -v -s -k --key /opt/ssl/server/csp-internal.key --cert /opt/ssl/server/csp-internal.crt https://anon.local.demo1-csp.athens.intrasoft-intl.private/apiversion

curl -v -s -k --key /opt/ssl/server/csp-internal.key --cert /opt/ssl/server/csp-internal.crt https://anon.local.demo1-csp.athens.intrasoft-intl.private/v1/ruleset/getAll


scp csp@central-csp:/opt/csp/anon/anon-server-0.2.0-SNAPSHOT-exec.jar anon-server-0.2.0-SNAPSHOT-exec.jar

scp csp@central-csp:/opt/csp/il/il-server-0.2.0-SNAPSHOT-exec.jar il-server-0.2.0-SNAPSHOT-exec.jar
scp csp@central-csp:/opt/csp/il/integration-tests-0.2.0-SNAPSHOT.jar integration-tests-0.2.0-SNAPSHOT.jar